    <item>
      <title>泰国央行维持利率不变，与政府的分歧加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-central-bank-holds-rate-deepening-rift-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行维持利率不变，拒绝满足总理斯雷塔·塔维辛降低借贷成本的要求，并表明与政府在支持东南亚第二大经济体的方式上分歧日益加大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-central-bank-holds-rate-deepening-rift-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克武器生产商 CSG 报告去年销售额创纪录 1.7 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/czech-arms-producer-csg-reports-record-1-7b-sales-for-last-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[武器生产商捷克斯洛伐克集团去年公布了创纪录的销售额和盈利能力，因为乌克兰战争增加了对这家总部位于布拉格的公司生产的重型弹药和战车的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/czech-arms-producer-csg-reports-record-1-7b-sales-for-last-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
