    <item>
      <title>由于债务稳步上升，惠誉将中国前景下调至负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fitch-cuts-china-outlook-to-negative-on-steady-rise-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级将中国的前景从稳定修正为负面，称政府可能会增加债务，以摆脱房地产驱动的经济放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fitch-cuts-china-outlook-to-negative-on-steady-rise-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:03:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七与我准备将 7-11 与原来的伊藤洋华堂店分开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/seven-i-climbs-on-reports-it-will-sell-ito-yokado-stores-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七与i Holdings Co. 正在考虑将伊藤洋华堂（该公司历史悠久的超市零售核心）上市，并最终将其从利润更高、增长更快的 7-11 特许经营权中剥离出来，集中精力将便利店打造成全球业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/seven-i-climbs-on-reports-it-will-sell-ito-yokado-stores-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中石油将建设液化天然气船队并扩大全球贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/petrochina-to-build-up-its-lng-fleet-and-expand-global-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的天然气供应商中国石油天然气集团公司将扩大其运输燃料的船队，以增强其作为全球天然气贸易商的作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/petrochina-to-build-up-its-lng-fleet-and-expand-global-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:03:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告指出美国库存增加，油价连续两天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份行业报告指出美国原油库存增加后，油价连续两天下跌，尽管中东紧张局势不断升温以及欧佩克+持续实施的限制措施预计将限制跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 23:15:34 GMT</pubDate>
